        <Parent_String>organ pipes (components) [300041705], pipes: aerophone components [300214931], aerophone components [300190947], sound device components [300205017], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
